      • DCD

        public DCD(int cid,
           int pid,
           int vid,
           int crpl,
           int features,
           java.util.ArrayList<DeviceInfo.Element> elements)
        Class constructor for the device composition data
        Parameters:
        cid - Contains a 16-bit company identifier assigned by the Bluetooth SIG
        pid - Contains a 16-bit vendor-assigned product identifier
        vid - Contains a 16-bit vendor-assigned product version identifier
        crpl - Contains a 16-bit value representing the minimum number of replay protection list entries in a device
        features - Contains a bit field indicating the device features
        elements - Contains a sequence of element descriptions
        See Also:
        DeviceInfo.Element
